        <p>(ABLC) a corporation organized and existing under Philippine laws with principal office address at Unit 1, Leonivo Bldg., cor. L. Sumulong Memorial Circle Manuel L. Quezon Ave., San oque, Antiplolo City, Rizal hereinafter called the "MORTGAGEE".</p>
